snippet.title: Super Dodgeball Beats - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
You’re invited to the craziest dodgeball contest ever! Get your groove on with Super Dodgeball Beats, the world’s first ever rhythm-sports game!

Download Super Dodgeball Beats for Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC (Steam) this August!
